    openerExtra: `Ameren Missouri ice-storm and derecho outage data for 2023-2024 shows 5-7 multi-day events affecting the St. Louis metro, including the July 2024 straight-line wind event that left 300,000 without power for 72 hours. Cold-rated lithium battery backups outlast sealed lead-acid by 3-4x in St. Louis January temperatures that regularly dip below 10F. LiftMaster Elite Series 8500W with factory lithium is the standard install across Ladue, Frontenac, and Town and Country.`,
