    smartHomeIntegration: `Detroit smart-home integration: LiftMaster MyQ dominates $400K+ Detroit-metro homes. MyQ integration with Ring, Amazon Key, and Apple HomeKit is standard in Birmingham and Bloomfield Hills. DTE Energy winter-storm outage frequency drives battery backup upgrades. Smart openers with cold-rated electronics perform better in sustained sub-freezing ambient. Licensed installer setup runs $75-$150.`,
